{"type": "article", "id": 26090, "title": "玻璃桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-28T07:10:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607121521W8FDz43kYbfqHsy2.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">这一系列的玻璃桌名为 Lady Hio，由 <a href=\"http://www.starck.com/en/\">Philippe Starck</a> 和 <a href=\"http://www.schito.com/\">S. Schito’s</a> 联合打造。管状的桌腿是它的一大亮点，用硼硅玻璃进行吹制，两端的阳极氧化铝合金则起到了连接桌面和固定的作用。整体造型非常优雅，并有黄、暖灰、橙三种颜色可供选择。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121519s30qHhNyeOFnta2E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121520mK14yNIQjlqbFUA7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121520UtgdJ1Ej7wnoFyPL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121521Ej0nUT6DXhFsofwg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}